sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as modelmesh-controller webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP plaintext
    participant Puller as Storage Helper (Puller)<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3/Minio Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh<br/>8033/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant RuntimeAdapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant ModelServer as Model Server<br/>8001/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant Service as modelmesh-serving Service<br/>8033/8008 TCP
    participant Client as Inference Client
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    rect rgb(230, 240, 250)
        Note over User,etcd: Flow 1: Model Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: POST Predictor CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate ServingRuntime<br/>K8s API cert auth
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
        K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Predictor CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: CR Event
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>etcd: Update model placement state<br/>Optional Basic Auth
    end

    rect rgb(240, 250, 230)
        Note over Puller,ModelServer: Flow 2: Model Loading
        Puller->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>AWS IAM or Access Keys
        S3-->>Puller: Model files
        Puller->>ModelServer: Load model via gRPC<br/>8001/TCP plaintext
        RuntimeAdapter->>ModelServer: Configure runtime<br/>8085/TCP gRPC plaintext
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Register model availability<br/>plaintext
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 3: Inference Request (gRPC)
        Client->>Service: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP plaintext
        Service->>ModelMesh: Forward inference request<br/>gRPC plaintext
        ModelMesh->>RuntimeAdapter: Route to model<br/>8085/TCP gRPC plaintext
        RuntimeAdapter->>ModelServer: Execute inference<br/>8001/TCP gRPC plaintext
        ModelServer-->>RuntimeAdapter: Prediction result
        RuntimeAdapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
        ModelMesh-->>Service: Response
        Service-->>Client: JSON/Protobuf response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 3: Inference Request (REST)
        Client->>Service: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTP 8008/TCP plaintext
        Service->>RESTProxy: Forward HTTP request
        RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: Translate to gRPC<br/>8033/TCP plaintext
        ModelMesh->>RuntimeAdapter: Route to model<br/>8085/TCP gRPC plaintext
        RuntimeAdapter->>ModelServer: Execute inference<br/>8001/TCP gRPC plaintext
        ModelServer-->>RuntimeAdapter: Prediction result
        RuntimeAdapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
        ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
        RESTProxy-->>Service: Translate to HTTP
        Service-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(250, 230, 250)
        Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics
        Prometheus->>Service: GET /metrics<br/>2112/TCP HTTP plaintext
        Service-->>Prometheus: Runtime pod metrics
    end
